ry of when this skill activates"\n}\n```\n\n\n<sandbox_execution_directive>\nIMPORTANT:【强制约束】所有脚本和文件操作必须在 AIO-Sandbox 中执行，禁止直接操作本地文件系统。\n此 Skill 资源已挂载至沙盒绝对路径：/mnt/skills/skill-creator/\n\n可用沙盒工具及正确用法：\n1. sandbox_execute_bash：执行 Shell 命令。参数：cmd（必填，字符串）、cwd（可选，工作目录绝对路径）、timeout（可选，秒）。\n   - 运行脚本示例：如需运行脚本scripts/xxx.py，则调用sandbox_execute_bash且参数为cmd="python /mnt/skills/skill-creator/scripts/xxx.py 参数"，如需可设 cwd="/mnt/skills/skill-creator"。\n   - 安装依赖：cmd="pip install 包名"，再重试任务。\n2. sandbox_file_operations：统一文件操作。参数：action（必填，\'read\'|\'write\'|\'list\'|\'find\'|\'replace\'|\'search\'）、path（必填，文件或目录绝对路径）、其余见工具说明。\n   - 读取单个文件：action="read", path="文件绝对路径"（示例：如需要获取reference/xxx.md，则调用工具sandbox_file_operations且参数为action="read", path="/mnt/skills/skill-creator/reference/xxx.md"）。\n   - 列出目录：action="list", path="目录绝对路径"（如 path="/mnt/skills/skill-creator/reference"），可选 recursive=true。\n   - 按模式查找文件：action="find", path="目录", pattern="*.md"。\n3. sandbox_str_replace_editor：编辑文件。参数：command（\'view\'|\'create\'|\'str_replace\'|\'insert\'）、path（文件路径）等。\n4. sandbox_execute_code：执行代码片段。参数：code（必填）、language（\'python\'|\'javascript\'）、timeout（可选）。\n</sandbox_execution_directive>\nYour personal goal is: 严格按照 skill-creator Skill 的操作规范，在 AIO-Sandbox 中完成任务'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '\nCurrent Task: 根据以下任务要求，使用你掌握的 Skill 操作规范完成任务。\n\n任务要求：\n{"skill_name": "analyze-hk-stock", "description": "分析港股的标准操作流程(SOP)，包含三个步骤：1. 查询实时行情 2. 查看近期新闻 3. 编写估值分析", "steps": ["查询指定港股的实时行情数据", "搜索该股票近一个月的相关新闻", "基于行情和新闻编写估值分析报告"], "output_file": "/workspace/output/analyze-hk-stock.yaml"}\n\n执行要求：\n1. 所有的操作必须在沙盒中执行，不得操作本地文件系统。\n   当前已挂载的目录：\n   - ./workspace:/workspace:rw（可读写，memory-save 写记忆文件到这里）\n   - ../skills:/mnt/skills:rw（可读写，skill-creator 写 SKILL.md 到这里）\n\n2. 记忆文件读写规范：\n   - 读取：用沙盒绝对路径 /workspace/<filename>（如 /workspace/user.md）\n   - 写入：同上，写前必须先 read 目标文件，确认无重复内容\n\n3. Skill 文件写入规范：\n   - 目录：/mnt/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md\n   - 注册：同时更新 /mnt/skills/load_skills.yaml\n\n4. 如遇依赖缺失，先在沙盒中安装再继续\n\nThis is the expected criteria for your final answer: 一份结构化的任务执行结果，按照任务要求中的json schema输出。\nyou MUST return the actual complete content as the final answer, not a summary.'}], 'temperature': 0.3, 'stop': ['\nObservation:'], 'tools': [{'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_get_browser_info', 'description': 'Get information about browser, like cdp url, viewport size, etc.\n\n    Args:\n        request (Dict): The incoming request context.', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_browser_screenshot', 'description': 'Take a screenshot of the current display.\n\n    Returns:\n        Image: A screenshot of the current display in JPEG format with metadata.', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_browser_execute_action', 'description': "Execute a browser action on the current display.\n\nArgs:\n    `action`: Dictionary containing `action_type` and relevant parameters.\n            The `action_type` determines which parameters are required.\n\nAction types and their parameters (auto-generated from models):\n    - CLICK: {action_type: 'CLICK', x: Optional?, y: Optional?, button: Literal?, num_clicks: Literal?}\n    - DOUBLE_CLICK: {action_type: 'DOUBLE_CLICK', x: Optional?, y: Optional?}\n    - DRAG_REL: {action_type: 'DRAG_REL', x_offset: float, y_offset: float}\n    - DRAG_TO: {action_type: 'DRAG_TO', x: float, y: float}\n    - HOTKEY: {action_type: 'HOTKEY', keys: List}\n    - KEY_DOWN: {action_type: 'KEY_DOWN', key: str}\n    - KEY_UP: {action_type: 'KEY_UP', key: str}\n    - MOUSE_DOWN: {action_type: 'MOUSE_DOWN', button: Literal?}\n    - MOUSE_UP: {action_type: 'MOUSE_UP', button: Literal?}\n    - MOVE_REL: {action_type: 'MOVE_REL', x_offset: float, y_offset: float}\n    - MOVE_TO: {action_type: 'MOVE_TO', x: float, y: float}\n    - PRESS: {action_type: 'PRESS', key: str}\n    - RIGHT_CLICK: {action_type: 'RIGHT_CLICK', x: Optional?, y: Optional?}\n    - SCROLL: {action_type: 'SCROLL', dx: int?, dy: int?}\n    - TYPING: {action_type: 'TYPING', text: str, use_clipboard: Optional?}\n    - WAIT: {action_type: 'WAIT', duration: float}\n\nReturns:\n    Dict containing `status` and `action_performed`\n\nRaises:\n    ValueError: If `action_type` is invalid or required parameters are missing", 'parameters': {'properties': {'action': {'additionalProperties': True, 'description': '', 'title': 'Action', 'type': 'object'}}, 'required': ['action'], 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_execute_code', 'description': "Execute code in Python or JavaScript runtime.\n\n    Args:\n        code: Code to execute\n        language: Programming language ('python', 'javascript')\n        timeout: Optional execution timeout in seconds\n\n    Returns:\n        Dict containing output, errors, and execution details", 'parameters': {'properties': {'code': {'description': '', 'title': 'Code', 'type': 'string'}, 'language': {'anyOf': [{}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': '', 'title': 'Language'}, 'timeout': {'anyOf': [{}, {'type': 'integer'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': '', 'title': 'Timeout'}}, 'required': ['code', 'language', 'timeout'], 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_file_operations', 'description': 'Unified file system operations tool for agents. `/tmp` and `/home/$USER` are fully accessible.\n\n    Args:\n        action: Operation type - "read", "write", "replace", "search", "find", "list"\n        path: File or directory path\n        content: Content for write/replace operations (or regex for search)\n        target: Target str