-guidelines\\n  #   path: ./brand-guidelines\\n  #   type: reference   # 只读指令，不执行脚本\\n  #   enabled: false\\n\\n  # HK Stock Analysis Skill\\n  - name: analyze-hk-stock\\n    path: ./analyze-hk-stock\\n    type: task\\n    enabled: true"}'}}]}, {'role': 'tool', 'tool_call_id': 'call_b477c619ef8f40db8a16fb78', 'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_str_replace_editor', 'content': '{\n  "command": "str_replace",\n  "path": "/mnt/skills/load_skills.yaml",\n  "output": "The file /mnt/skills/load_skills.yaml has been edited. Here\'s the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of /mnt/skills/load_skills.yaml:\\n    33\\t    type: task       # 扫描 + 报告 + 清理，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    34\\t    enabled: true\\n    35\\t\\n    36\\t  # 预留：参考型 Skill 示例（如品牌规范、代码规范等）\\n    37\\t  # - name: brand-guidelines\\n    38\\t  #   path: ./brand-guidelines\\n    39\\t  #   type: reference   # 只读指令，不执行脚本\\n    40\\t  #   enabled: false\\n    41\\t\\n    42\\t  # HK Stock Analysis Skill\\n    43\\t  - name: analyze-hk-stock\\n    44\\t    path: ./analyze-hk-stock\\n    45\\t    type: task\\n    46\\t    enabled: true\\n    47\\t\\nReview the changes and make sure they are as expected. Edit the file again if necessary.",\n  "error": null,\n  "prev_exist": true,\n  "old_content": "# Skill 清单：m2l16 Skills 生态课程演示\\n#\\n# type 字段区分 Skill 的执行方式：\\n#   task      → 触发独立 Sub-Crew 在 AIO-Sandbox 中执行（需要代码运行）\\n#   reference → 直接注入指令到调用方上下文，不启动 Sub-Crew（只读规范类）\\n#\\n# 💡 核心点：type 写在这里，不改 Anthropic 官方 SKILL.md 文件\\n\\nskills:\\n  - name: pdf\\n    path: ./pdf\\n    type: task       # 需要代码执行（pypdf / pdfplumber）\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: docx\\n    path: ./docx\\n    type: task       # 需要代码执行（docx-js / pandoc）\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  # m3l20：文件系统记忆 Skills\\n  - name: memory-save\\n    path: ./memory-save\\n    type: task       # 写入 workspace/ 文件，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: skill-creator\\n    path: ./skill-creator\\n    type: task       # 写入 skills/ 目录，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: memory-governance\\n    path: ./memory-governance\\n    type: task       # 扫描 + 报告 + 清理，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  # 预留：参考型 Skill 示例（如品牌规范、代码规范等）\\n  # - name: brand-guidelines\\n  #   path: ./brand-guidelines\\n  #   type: reference   # 只读指令，不执行脚本\\n  #   enabled: false\\n",\n  "new_content": "# Skill 清单：m2l16 Skills 生态课程演示\\n#\\n# type 字段区分 Skill 的执行方式：\\n#   task      → 触发独立 Sub-Crew 在 AIO-Sandbox 中执行（需要代码运行）\\n#   reference → 直接注入指令到调用方上下文，不启动 Sub-Crew（只读规范类）\\n#\\n# 💡 核心点：type 写在这里，不改 Anthropic 官方 SKILL.md 文件\\n\\nskills:\\n  - name: pdf\\n    path: ./pdf\\n    type: task       # 需要代码执行（pypdf / pdfplumber）\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: docx\\n    path: ./docx\\n    type: task       # 需要代码执行（docx-js / pandoc）\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  # m3l20：文件系统记忆 Skills\\n  - name: memory-save\\n    path: ./memory-save\\n    type: task       # 写入 workspace/ 文件，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: skill-creator\\n    path: ./skill-creator\\n    type: task       # 写入 skills/ 目录，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: memory-governance\\n    path: ./memory-governance\\n    type: task       # 扫描 + 报告 + 清理，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  # 预留：参考型 Skill 示例（如品牌规范、代码规范等）\\n  # - name: brand-guidelines\\n  #   path: ./brand-guidelines\\n  #   type: reference   # 只读指令，不执行脚本\\n  #   enabled: false\\n\\n  # HK Stock Analysis Skill\\n  - name: analyze-hk-stock\\n    path: ./analyze-hk-stock\\n    type: task\\n    enabled: true\\n",\n  "success": true\n}'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Analyze the tool result. If requirements are met, provide the Final Answer. Otherwise, call the next tool. Deliver only the answer without meta-commentary.'}]
