': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_str_replace_editor', 'content': '{\n  "command": "str_replace",\n  "path": "/mnt/skills/load_skills.yaml",\n  "output": "The file /mnt/skills/load_skills.yaml has been edited. Here\'s the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of /mnt/skills/load_skills.yaml:\\n    33\\t    type: task       # 扫描 + 报告 + 清理，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    34\\t    enabled: true\\n    35\\t\\n    36\\t  # 预留：参考型 Skill 示例（如品牌规范、代码规范等）\\n    37\\t  # - name: brand-guidelines\\n    38\\t  #   path: ./brand-guidelines\\n    39\\t  #   type: reference   # 只读指令，不执行脚本\\n    40\\t  #   enabled: false\\n    41\\t\\n    42\\t  # HK Stock Analysis Skill\\n    43\\t  - name: analyze-hk-stock\\n    44\\t    path: ./analyze-hk-stock\\n    45\\t    type: task\\n    46\\t    enabled: true\\n    47\\t\\nReview the changes and make sure they are as expected. Edit the file again if necessary.",\n  "error": null,\n  "prev_exist": true,\n  "old_content": "# Skill 清单：m2l16 Skills 生态课程演示\\n#\\n# type 字段区分 Skill 的执行方式：\\n#   task      → 触发独立 Sub-Crew 在 AIO-Sandbox 中执行（需要代码运行）\\n#   reference → 直接注入指令到调用方上下文，不启动 Sub-Crew（只读规范类）\\n#\\n# 💡 核心点：type 写在这里，不改 Anthropic 官方 SKILL.md 文件\\n\\nskills:\\n  - name: pdf\\n    path: ./pdf\\n    type: task       # 需要代码执行（pypdf / pdfplumber）\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: docx\\n    path: ./docx\\n    type: task       # 需要代码执行（docx-js / pandoc）\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  # m3l20：文件系统记忆 Skills\\n  - name: memory-save\\n    path: ./memory-save\\n    type: task       # 写入 workspace/ 文件，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: skill-creator\\n    path: ./skill-creator\\n    type: task       # 写入 skills/ 目录，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: memory-governance\\n    path: ./memory-governance\\n    type: task       # 扫描 + 报告 + 清理，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  # 预留：参考型 Skill 示例（如品牌规范、代码规范等）\\n  # - name: brand-guidelines\\n  #   path: ./brand-guidelines\\n  #   type: reference   # 只读指令，不执行脚本\\n  #   enabled: false\\n",\n  "new_content": "# Skill 清单：m2l16 Skills 生态课程演示\\n#\\n# type 字段区分 Skill 的执行方式：\\n#   task      → 触发独立 Sub-Crew 在 AIO-Sandbox 中执行（需要代码运行）\\n#   reference → 直接注入指令到调用方上下文，不启动 Sub-Crew（只读规范类）\\n#\\n# 💡 核心点：type 写在这里，不改 Anthropic 官方 SKILL.md 文件\\n\\nskills:\\n  - name: pdf\\n    path: ./pdf\\n    type: task       # 需要代码执行（pypdf / pdfplumber）\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: docx\\n    path: ./docx\\n    type: task       # 需要代码执行（docx-js / pandoc）\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  # m3l20：文件系统记忆 Skills\\n  - name: memory-save\\n    path: ./memory-save\\n    type: task       # 写入 workspace/ 文件，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: skill-creator\\n    path: ./skill-creator\\n    type: task       # 写入 skills/ 目录，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  - name: memory-governance\\n    path: ./memory-governance\\n    type: task       # 扫描 + 报告 + 清理，需要沙盒 MCP 执行\\n    enabled: true\\n\\n  # 预留：参考型 Skill 示例（如品牌规范、代码规范等）\\n  # - name: brand-guidelines\\n  #   path: ./brand-guidelines\\n  #   type: reference   # 只读指令，不执行脚本\\n  #   enabled: false\\n\\n  # HK Stock Analysis Skill\\n  - name: analyze-hk-stock\\n    path: ./analyze-hk-stock\\n    type: task\\n    enabled: true\\n",\n  "success": true\n}'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Analyze the tool result. If requirements are met, provide the Final Answer. Otherwise, call the next tool. Deliver only the answer without meta-commentary.'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': None, 'tool_calls': [{'id': 'call_013d904a325e475ba3d005ce', 'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_file_operations', 'arguments': '{"action": "read", "path": "/mnt/skills/analyze-hk-stock/SKILL.md"}'}}]}, {'role': 'tool', 'tool_call_id': 'call_013d904a325e475ba3d005ce', 'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_file_operations', 'content': '{\n  "action": "read",\n  "path": "/mnt/skills/analyze-hk-stock/SKILL.md",\n  "content": "---\\nname: analyze-hk-stock\\ndescription: Use this skill when the user asks to analyze Hong Kong stocks, research HK companies, or evaluate HK investment opportunities. Activate whenever 港股 or HK stock analysis is needed.\\n---\\n\\n## Overview\\nThis skill provides a standardized workflow for analyzing Hong Kong-listed stocks. It follows a three-step process: gathering real-time market data, collecting recent news coverage, and synthesizing a valuation analysis report.\\n\\n## Workflow Steps\\n\\n### Step 1: Query Real-time Market Data\\n- Use browser tools to navigate to financial websites (like Yahoo Finance, Bloomberg, or HKEX) to retrieve current stock price, trading volume, market cap, and key metrics for the specified HK stock ticker.\\n- Ensure the data includes at least: current price, daily change %, 52-week range, P/E ratio, and dividend yield.\\n\\n### Step 2: Search Recent News\\n- Use browser tools to search for news articles about the specific stock from the past month.\\n- Focus on credible financial news sources and official company announcements.\\n- Collect headlines, publication dates, and brief summaries of relevant news items.\\n\\n### Step 3: Generate Valuation Analysis Report\\n- Synthesize the market data and news findings into a structured valuation analysis.\\n- The report should include:\\n  - Current market position\\n  - Recent developments (from news)\\n  - Key valuation metrics interpretation\\n  - Risk factors identified\\n  - Investment outlook summary\\n\\n## Output Format\\nThe final output should be a comprehensive markdown report with the following structure:\\n\\n# [Stock Name] ([Ticker]) - HK Stock Analysis\\n\\n## Executive Summary\\nBrief overview of current status and investment thesis.\\n\\n## Market Data\\n- Current Price: [price]\\n- Daily Change: [change %]\\n- Market Cap: [market cap]\\n- P/E Ratio: [P/E]\\n- Dividend Yield: [yield %]\\n- 52-Week Range: [low] - [high]\\n\\n## Recent News Summary\\n- [Date] - [Headline]: [Brief summary]\\n- [Date] - [Headline]: [Brief summary]\\n(Include 3-5 most relevant recent news items)\\n\\n## Valuation Analysis\\nDetailed analysis combining market data and news context.\\n\\n## Risk Factors\\nKey risks identified from market conditions and news.\\n\\n## Investment Outlook\\nShort-term and long-term outlook assessment.\\n\\n## Allowed Tools\\nThis skill requires access to web browsing capabilities to gather real-time financial data and news. The implementation uses browser navigation and content extraction rather than direct API calls to ensure data freshness and availability across different financial platforms.",\n  "success": true\n}'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Analyze the tool result. If requirements are met, provide the Final Answer. Otherwise, call the next tool. Deliver only the answer without meta-commentary.'}], 'temperature': 0.3, 'stop': ['\nObservation:'], 'tools': [{'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_get_browser_info', 'description': 'Get information about browser, like cdp url, viewport size, etc.\n\n    Args:\n        request (Dict): The incoming request context.', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_browser_screenshot', 'description': 'Take a screenshot of the current display.\n\n    Returns:\n        Image: A screenshot of the current display in JPEG format with metadata.', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_browser_execute_action', 'description': "Execute a browser action on the current display.\n\nArgs:\n    `action`: Dictionary containing `action_type` and relevant parameters.\n            The `action_type` determines which parameters are required.\n\nAction types and their parameters (auto-generated from models):\n    - CLICK: {action_type: 'CLICK', x: Optional?, y: Optional?, button: Literal?, num_clicks: Literal?}\n    - DOUBLE_CLICK: {action_type: 'DOUBLE_CLICK', x: Optional?, y: Optional?}\n    - DRAG_REL: {action_type: 'DRAG_REL', x_offset: float, y_offset: float}\n    - DRAG_TO: {action_type: 'DRAG_TO', x: float, y: float}\n    - HOTKEY: {action_type: 'HOTKEY', keys: List}\n    - KEY_DOWN: {action_type: 'KEY_DOWN', key: str}\n    - KEY_UP: {action_type: 'KEY_UP', key: str}\n    - MOUSE_DOWN: {action_type: 'MOUSE_DOWN', button: Literal?}\n    - MOUSE_UP: {action_type: 'MOUSE_UP', button: Literal?}\n    - MOVE_REL: {action_type: 'MOVE_REL', x_offset: float, y_offset: float}\n    - MOVE_TO: {action_type: 'MOVE_TO', x: float, y: float}\n    - PRESS: {action_type: 'PRESS', key: str}\n    - RIGHT_CLICK: {action_type: 'RIGHT_CLICK', x: Optional?, y: Optional?}\n    - SCROLL: {action_type: 'SCROLL', dx: int?, dy: int?}\n    - TYPING: {action_type: 'TYPING', text: str, use_clipboard: Optional?}\n    - WAIT: {action_type: 'WAIT', duration: float}\n\nReturns:\n    Dict containing `status` and `action_performed`\n\nRaises:\n    ValueError: If `action_type` is invalid or required parameters are missing", 'parameters': {'properties': {'action': {'additionalProperties': True, 'description': '', 'title': 'Action', 'type': 'object'}}, 'required': ['action'], 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_execute_code', 'description': "Execute code in Python or JavaScript runtime.\n\n    Args:\n        code: Code to execute\n        language: Programming language ('python', 'javascript')\n        timeout: Optional execution timeout in seconds\n\n    Returns:\n        Dict containing output, errors, and execution details", 'parameters': {'properties': {'code': {'description': '', 'title': 'Code', 'type': 'string'}, 'language': {'anyOf': [{}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': '', 'title': 'Language'}, 'timeout': {'anyOf': [{}, {'type': 'integer'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': '', 'title'