    "name": "localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_file_operations",
    "content": "{\n  \"action\": \"read\",\n  \"path\": \"/mnt/skills/analyze-hk-stock/SKILL.md\",\n  \"content\": \"---\\nname: analyze-hk-stock\\ndescription: Use this skill when the user asks to analyze Hong Kong stocks, research HK companies, or evaluate HK investment opportunities. Activate whenever 港股 or HK stock analysis is needed.\\n---\\n\\n## Overview\\nThis skill provides a standardized workflow for analyzing Hong Kong-listed stocks. It follows a three-step process: gathering real-time market data, collecting recent news coverage, and synthesizing a valuation analysis report.\\n\\n## Workflow Steps\\n\\n### Step 1: Query Real-time Market Data\\n- Use browser tools to navigate to financial websites (like Yahoo Finance, Bloomberg, or HKEX) to retrieve current stock price, trading volume, market cap, and key metrics for the specified HK stock ticker.\\n- Ensure the data includes at least: current price, daily change %, 52-week range, P/E ratio, and dividend yield.\\n\\n### Step 2: Search Recent News\\n- Use browser tools to search for news articles about the specific stock from the past month.\\n- Focus on credible financial news sources and official company announcements.\\n- Collect headlines, publication dates, and brief summaries of relevant news items.\\n\\n### Step 3: Generate Valuation Analysis Report\\n- Synthesize the market data and news findings into a structured valuation analysis.\\n- The report should include:\\n  - Current market position\\n  - Recent developments (from news)\\n  - Key valuation metrics interpretation\\n  - Risk factors identified\\n  - Investment outlook summary\\n\\n## Output Format\\nThe final output should be a comprehensive markdown report with the following structure:\\n\\n# [Stock Name] ([Ticker]) - HK Stock Analysis\\n\\n## Executive Summary\\nBrief overview of current status and investment thesis.\\n\\n## Market Data\\n- Current Price: [price]\\n- Daily Change: [change %]\\n- Market Cap: [market cap]\\n- P/E Ratio: [P/E]\\n- Dividend Yield: [yield %]\\n- 52-Week Range: [low] - [high]\\n\\n## Recent News Summary\\n- [Date] - [Headline]: [Brief summary]\\n- [Date] - [Headline]: [Brief summary]\\n(Include 3-5 most relevant recent news items)\\n\\n## Valuation Analysis\\nDetailed analysis combining market data and news context.\\n\\n## Risk Factors\\nKey risks identified from market conditions and news.\\n\\n## Investment Outlook\\nShort-term and long-term outlook assessment.\\n\\n## Allowed Tools\\nThis skill requires access to web browsing capabilities to gather real-time financial data and news. The implementation uses browser navigation and content extraction rather than direct API calls to ensure data freshness and availability across different financial platforms.\",\n  \"success\": true\n}"
  },
