tion', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_read_links', 'description': 'Get all links on the current page', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_new_tab', 'description': 'Open a new tab', 'parameters': {'properties': {'url': {'description': 'URL to open in the new tab', 'title': 'Url', 'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['url'], 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_tab_list', 'description': 'Get the list of tabs', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_switch_tab', 'description': 'Switch to a specific tab', 'parameters': {'properties': {'index': {'description': 'Tab index to switch to', 'title': 'Index', 'type': 'number'}}, 'required': ['index'], 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_close_tab', 'description': 'Close the current tab', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_evaluate', 'description': 'Execute JavaScript in the browser console', 'parameters': {'properties': {'script': {'description': 'JavaScript code to execute, () => { /* code */ }', 'title': 'Script', 'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['script'], 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_vision_screen_capture', 'description': 'Take a screenshot of the current page for vision mode', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_vision_screen_click', 'description': 'Click left mouse button on the page with vision and snapshot, before calling this tool, you should call `browser_vision_screen_capture` first only once, fallback to `browser_click` if failed', 'parameters': {'properties': {'factors': {'anyOf': [{'items': {}, 'type': 'array'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Vision model coordinate system scaling factors [width_factor, height_factor] for coordinate space normalization. Transformation formula: x = (x_model * screen_width * width_factor) / width_factor y = (y_model * screen_height * height_factor) / height_factor where x_model, y_model are normalized model output coordinates (0-1), screen_width/height are screen dimensions, width_factor/height_factor are quantization factors, If the factors are unknown, leave it blank. Most models do not require this parameter.', 'title': 'Factors'}, 'x': {'description': 'X pixel coordinate', 'title': 'X', 'type': 'number'}, 'y': {'description': 'Y pixel coordinate', 'title': 'Y', 'type': 'number'}}, 'required': ['factors', 'x', 'y'], 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_get_download_list', 'description': 'Get the list of downloaded files', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_screenshot', 'description': 'Take a screenshot of the current page or a specific element', 'parameters': {'properties': {'name': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'string'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Name for the screenshot', 'title': 'Name'}, 'selector': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'string'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'CSS selector for element to screenshot', 'title': 'Selector'}, 'index': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'number'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'index of the element to screenshot', 'title': 'Index'}, 'width': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'number'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Width in pixels (default: viewport width)', 'title': 'Width'}, 'height': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'number'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Height in pixels (default: viewport height)', 'title': 'Height'}, 'fullPage': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'boolean'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Full page screenshot (default: false)', 'title': 'Fullpage'}, 'highlight': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'boolean'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Highlight the element', 'title': 'Highlight'}}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'required': ['name', 'selector', 'index', 'width', 'height', 'fullPage', 'highlight']}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_click', 'description': 'Click an element on the page, before using the tool, use `browser_get_clickable_elements` to get the index of the element, but not call `browser_get_clickable_elements` multiple times', 'parameters': {'properties': {'index': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'number'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Index of the element to click', 'title': 'Index'}}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'required': ['index']}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_select', 'description': "Select an element on the page with index, Either 'index' or 'selector' must be provided", 'parameters': {'properties': {'index': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'number'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Index of the element to select', 'title': 'Index'}, 'selector': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'string'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'CSS selector for element to select', 'title': 'Selector'}, 'value': {'description': 'Value to select', 'title': 'Value', 'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['index', 'selector', 'value'], 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_hover', 'description': "Hover an element on the page, Either 'index' or 'selector' must be provided", 'parameters': {'properties': {'index': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'number'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Index of the element to hover', 'title': 'Index'}, 'selector': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'string'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'CSS selector for element to hover', 'title': 'Selector'}}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'required': ['index', 'selector']}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_get_clickable_elements', 'description': "Get the clickable or hoverable or selectable elements on the current page, don't call this tool multiple times", 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_scroll', 'description': 'Scroll the page', 'parameters': {'properties': {'amount': {'anyOf': [{'type': 'number'}, {'type': 'null'}], 'default': None, 'description': 'Pixels to scroll (positive for down, negative for up), if the amount is not provided, scroll to the bottom of the page', 'title': 'Amount'}}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'required': ['amount']}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_close', 'description': 'Close the browser when the task is done and the browser is not needed anymore', 'parameters': {'properties': {}, 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_browser_press_key', 'description': 'Press a key on the keyboard', 'parameters': {'properties': {'key': {'description': 'Name of the key to press or a character to generate, such as Enter, Tab, Escape, Backspace, Delete, Insert, F1, F2, F3, F4, F5, F6, F7, F8, F9, F10, F11, F12, ArrowLeft, ArrowRight, ArrowUp, ArrowDown, PageUp, PageDown, Home, End, ShiftLeft, ShiftRight, ControlLeft, ControlRight, AltLeft, AltRight, MetaLeft, MetaRight, CapsLock, PrintScreen, ScrollLock, Pause, ContextMenu', 'title': 'Key', 'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['key'], 'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False}, 'strict': True}}]} payload=[{'role': 'system', 'content': 'You are MEMORY-GOVERNANCE Skill 执行专家. 你是一位专精于 memory-governance 文件处理的 AI 专家。\n你掌握以下操作规范，请严格遵循：\n\n\n# memory-governance：记忆与 Skill 治理\n\n## 概述\n\n定期审计 workspace 记忆文件和 skills/ 目录，输出结构化分析报告，\n用户确认后执行清理操作，防止记忆腐化和技能目录膨胀。\n\n执行频率：每月一次，或 memory-save 检测到 memory.md 超过 180 行时主动触发。\n\n**为什么需要治理：**\n混乱的长记忆是整个应用的杀手。记忆腐化有两条路径：\n1. **信息过时**：user.md 有旧偏好、memory.md 有死链（指向已删除文件）\n2. **索引爆炸**：memory.md 不断追加接近 200 行、skills/ 有重复功能的 Skill\n\n## 步骤\n\n### 第一步：扫描，生成 JSON 分析报告\n\n读取以下文件，进行结构化分析：\n- `/workspace/memory.md`：检查行数、死链（索引条目对应文件不存在）\n- `/workspace/*.md`：检查 topic 文件的最后修改时间\n- `/mnt/skills/load_skills.yaml`：检查已注册 Skill 列表\n- `/mnt/skills/*/SKILL.md`：检查 description 是否有重叠\n\n生成内部 JSON 分析（精确，便于后续操作）：\n\n```json\n{\n  "memory_issues": [\n    {\n      "type": "dead_link",\n      "entry": "投资记录 → memory_invest.md",\n      "reason": "文件不存在"\n    },\n    {\n      "type": "near_limit",\n      "current_lines": 178,\n      "limit": 200,\n      "action": "trigger_governance"\n    }\n  ],\n  "topic_files": [\n    {\n      "file": "memory_2023_project.md",\n      "last_modified": "2023-11-01",\n      "days_since": 480,\n      "action": "archive"\n    }\n  ],\n  "skill_issues": [\n    {\n      "type": "duplicate",\n      "skills": ["analyze-stock", "hk-stock-analysis"],\n      "recommendation": "merge into analyze-hk-stock"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 第二步：生成 MD 治理报告（给用户审批）\n\n将 JSON 分析转换为可读 Markdown，写入 `/workspace/memory_governance_report.md`：\n\n```markdown\n# 记忆治理报告 — <日期>\n\n## memory.md 状态\n- 当前行数：<n> 行（上限 200 行）\n- 状态：<正常 / 警告 / 已超限>\n\n## 发现的问题\n\n### 死链（共 <n> 条）\n| 条目 | 原因 | 建议操作 |\n|------|------|---------|\n| 投资记录 → memory_invest.md | 文件不存在 | 删除此条目 |\n\n### 过期 Topic 文件（<n> 个）\n| 文件 | 最后更新 | 建议操作 |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| memory_2023_project.md | 480 天前 | 归档或删除 |\n\n### Skill 重叠（<n> 组）\n| Skill 1 | Skill 2 | 建议 |\n|---------|---------|------|\n| analyze-stock | hk-stock-analysis | 合并为 analyze-hk-stock |\n\n## 建议操作清单\n- [ ] 删除 memory.md 中 <n> 条死链\n- [ ] 归档 <n> 个过期 topic 文件到 /workspace/archive/\n- [ ] 合并重叠 Skill\n```\n\n### 第三步：等待用户确认，再执行清理\n\n**CRITICAL：不得在用户确认前执行任何删除或修改操作**\n原因：治理报告可能误判（如文件确实存在但路径格式不同），用户确认是最后防线。\n报告生成后，明确提示用户："请确认以上操作清单，回复\'确认执行\'后我将开始清理。"\n\n用户确认后，按清单逐项执行：\n1. 从 memory.md 删除死链条目\n2. 将过期 topic 文件移动到 `/workspace/archive/`（不删除，保留历史）\n3. 按用户指示合并或禁用重叠 Skill\n\n**CRITICAL：执行后读取验证**\n每项操作后读取对应文件，确认变更已落盘、无误删。\n\n\n<sandbox_execution_directive>\nIMPORTANT:【强制约束】所有脚本和文件操作必须在 AIO-Sandbox 中执行，禁止直接操作本地文件系统。\n此 Skill 资源已挂载至沙盒绝对路径：/mnt/skills/memory-governance/\n\n可用沙盒工具及正确用法：\n1. sandbox_execute_bash：执行 Shell 命令。参数：cmd（必填，字符串）、cwd（可选，工作目录绝对路径）、timeout（可选，秒）。\n   - 运行脚本示例：如需运行脚本scripts/xxx.py，则调用sandbox_execute_bash且参数为cmd="python /mnt/skills/memory-governance/scripts/xxx.py 参数"，如需可设 cwd="/mnt/skills/memory-governance"。\n   - 安装依赖：cmd="pip install 包名"，再重试任务。\n2. sandbox_file_operations：统一文件操作。参数：action（必填，\'read\'|\'write\'|\'list\'|\'find\'|\'replace\'|\'search\'）、path（必填，文件或目录绝对路径）、其余见工具说明。\n   - 读取单个文件：action="read", path="文件绝对路径"（示例：如需要获取reference/xxx.md，则调用工具sandbox_file_operations且参数为action="read", path="/mnt/skills/memory-governance/reference/xxx.md"）。\n   - 列出目录：action="list", path="目录绝对路径"（如 path="/mnt/skills/memory-governance/reference"），可选 recursive=true。\n   - 按模式查找文件：action="find", path="目录", pattern="*.md"。\n3. sandbox_str_replace_editor：编辑文件。参数：command（\'view\'|\'create\'|\'str_replace\'|\'insert\'）、path（文件路径）等。\n4. sandbox_execute_code：执行代码片段。参数：code（必填）、language（\'python\'|\'javascript\'）、timeout（可选）。\n</sandbox_execution_directive>\nYour p