l-creator\\\", \\\"enabled\\\": True},\\n    {\\\"name\\\": \\\"memory-governance\\\", \\\"enabled\\\": True},\\n    {\\\"name\\\": \\\"analyze-hk-stock\\\", \\\"enabled\\\": True}\\n]\\n\\n# Check for potential duplicates\\n# Based on the loaded skills, we have analyze-hk-stock which seems to be a specific implementation\\n# No obvious duplicates found in the current skill list, but we'll check descriptions\\nskill_issues = []\\n\\n# Create analysis report\\nanalysis_report = {\\n    \\\"memory_issues\\\": memory_issues,\\n    \\\"topic_files\\\": topic_files,\\n    \\\"skill_issues\\\": skill_issues\\n}\\n\\nanalysis_report\", \"language\": \"python\", \"timeout\": \"30\"}"
