d",\n      "is_directory": false,\n      "size": 171367,\n      "modified_time": "1772458042",\n      "permissions": null,\n      "extension": ".xsd"\n    },\n    {\n      "name": "wml.xsd",\n      "path": "/mnt/skills/pptx/scripts/office/schemas/ISO-IEC29500-4_2016/wml.xsd",\n      "is_directory": false,\n      "size": 171367,\n      "modified_time": "1772458042",\n      "permissions": null,\n      "extension": ".xsd"\n    },\n    {\n      "name": "wml.xsd",\n      "path": "/mnt/skills/docx/scripts/office/schemas/ISO-IEC29500-4_2016/wml.xsd",\n      "is_directory": false,\n      "size": 171367,\n      "modified_time": "1772458042",\n      "permissions": null,\n      "extension": ".xsd"\n    },\n    {\n      "name": "xlsx",\n      "path": "/mnt/skills/xlsx",\n      "is_directory": true,\n      "size": null,\n      "modified_time": "1772458050",\n      "permissions": null,\n      "extension": null\n    },\n    {\n      "name": "xml.xsd",\n      "path": "/mnt/skills/xlsx/scripts/office/schemas/ISO-IEC29500-4_2016/xml.xsd",\n      "is_directory": false,\n      "size": 4646,\n      "modified_time": "1772458042",\n      "permissions": null,\n      "extension": ".xsd"\n    },\n    {\n      "name": "xml.xsd",\n      "path": "/mnt/skills/pptx/scripts/office/schemas/ISO-IEC29500-4_2016/xml.xsd",\n      "is_directory": false,\n      "size": 4646,\n      "modified_time": "1772458042",\n      "permissions": null,\n      "extension": ".xsd"\n    },\n    {\n      "name": "xml.xsd",\n      "path": "/mnt/skills/docx/scripts/office/schemas/ISO-IEC29500-4_2016/xml.xsd",\n      "is_directory": false,\n      "size": 4646,\n      "modified_time": "1772458042",\n      "permissions": null,\n      "extension": ".xsd"\n    }\n  ],\n  "total_count": 259,\n  "directory_count": 47,\n  "file_count": 212,\n  "success": true\n}'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Analyze the tool result. If requirements are met, provide the Final Answer. Otherwise, call the next tool. Deliver only the answer without meta-commentary.'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': None, 'tool_calls': [{'id': 'call_23df4a1104254274ac24d448', 'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_file_operations', 'arguments': '{"action": "read", "path": "/mnt/skills/analyze-hk-stock/SKILL.md"}'}}]}, {'role': 'tool', 'tool_call_id': 'call_23df4a1104254274ac24d448', 'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_file_operations', 'content': '{\n  "action": "read",\n  "path": "/mnt/skills/analyze-hk-stock/SKILL.md",\n  "content": "---\\nname: analyze-hk-stock\\ndescription: Use this skill when the user asks to analyze Hong Kong stocks, research HK companies, or evaluate HK investment opportunities. Activate whenever 港股 or HK stock analysis is needed.\\n---\\n\\n## Overview\\nThis skill provides a standardized workflow for analyzing Hong Kong-listed stocks. It follows a three-step process: gathering real-time market data, collecting recent news coverage, and synthesizing a valuation analysis report.\\n\\n## Workflow Steps\\n\\n### Step 1: Query Real-time Market Data\\n- Use browser tools to navigate to financial websites (like Yahoo Finance, Bloomberg, or HKEX) to retrieve current stock price, trading volume, market cap, and key metrics for the specified HK stock ticker.\\n- Ensure the data includes at least: current price, daily change %, 52-week range, P/E ratio, and dividend yield.\\n\\n### Step 2: Search Recent News\\n- Use browser tools to search for news articles about the specific stock from the past month.\\n- Focus on credible financial news sources and official company announcements.\\n- Collect headlines, publication dates, and brief summaries of relevant news items.\\n\\n### Step 3: Generate Valuation Analysis Report\\n- Synthesize the market data and news findings into a structured valuation analysis.\\n- The report should include:\\n  - Current market position\\n  - Recent developments (from news)\\n  - Key valuation metrics interpretation\\n  - Risk factors identified\\n  - Investment outlook summary\\n\\n## Output Format\\nThe final output should be a comprehensive markdown report with the following structure:\\n\\n# [Stock Name] ([Ticker]) - HK Stock Analysis\\n\\n## Executive Summary\\nBrief overview of current status and investment thesis.\\n\\n## Market Data\\n- Current Price: [price]\\n- Daily Change: [change %]\\n- Market Cap: [market cap]\\n- P/E Ratio: [P/E]\\n- Dividend Yield: [yield %]\\n- 52-Week Range: [low] - [high]\\n\\n## Recent News Summary\\n- [Date] - [Headline]: [Brief summary]\\n- [Date] - [Headline]: [Brief summary]\\n(Include 3-5 most relevant recent news items)\\n\\n## Valuation Analysis\\nDetailed analysis combining market data and news context.\\n\\n## Risk Factors\\nKey risks identified from market conditions and news.\\n\\n## Investment Outlook\\nShort-term and long-term outlook assessment.\\n\\n## Allowed Tools\\nThis skill requires access to web browsing capabilities to gather real-time financial data and news. The implementation uses browser navigation and content extraction rather than direct API calls to ensure data freshness and availability across different financial platforms.",\n  "success": true\n}'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Analyze the tool result. If requirements are met, provide the Final Answer. Otherwise, call the next tool. Deliver only the answer without meta-commentary.'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': None, 'tool_calls': [{'id': 'call_71e6fd3ab626438299953ce8', 'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_file_operations', 'arguments': '{"action": "read", "path": "/mnt/skills/memory-governance/SKILL.md"}'}}]}, {'role': 'tool', 'tool_call_id': 'call_71e6fd3ab626438299953ce8', 'name': 'localhost_8022_mcp_sandbox_file_operations', 'content': '{\n  "action": "read",\n  "path": "/mnt/skills/memory-governance/SKILL.md",\n  "content": "---\\nname: memory-governance\\ndescription: >\\n  Use this skill to audit and clean up workspace memory files and the skills\\n  directory. Activate when:\\n  - memory.md is approaching 150+ lines (Bootstrap limit is 200)\\n  - User requests a memory cleanup or audit\\n  - Skills directory has grown large and may contain duplicates or stale entries\\n  - memory-save reports that memory.md is near the limit\\n\\n  Do NOT activate for: normal conversation, saving new memories (use\\n  memory-save), creating new skills (use skill-creator).\\nallowed-tools:\\n  - Read\\n  - Write\\n  - Bash\\n---\\n\\n# memory-governance：记忆与 Skill 治理\\n\\n## 概述\\n\\n定期审计 workspace 记忆文件和 skills/ 目录，输出结构化分析报告，\\n用户确认后执行清理操作，防止记忆腐化和技能目录膨胀。\\n\\n执行频率：每月一次，或 memory-save 检测到 memory.md 超过 180 行时主动触发。\\n\\n**为什么需要治理：**\\n混乱的长记忆是整个应用的杀手。记忆腐化有两条路径：\\n1. **信息过时**：user.md 有旧偏好、memory.md 有死链（指向已删除文件）\\n2. **索引爆炸**：memory.md 不断追加接近 200 行、skills/ 有重复功能的 Skill\\n\\n## 步骤\\n\\n### 第一步：扫描，生成 JSON 分析报告\\n\\n读取以下文件，进行结构化分析：\\n- `/workspace/memory.md`：检查行数、死链（索引条目对应文件不存在）\\n- `/workspace/*.md`：检查 topic 文件的最后修改时间\\n- `/mnt/skills/load_skills.yaml`：检查已注册 Skill 列表\\n- `/mnt/skills/*/SKILL.md`：检查 description 是否有重叠\\n\\n生成内部 JSON 分析（精确，便于后续操作）：\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\"memory_issues\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"type\\": \\"dead_link\\",\\n      \\"entry\\": \\"投资记录 → memory_invest.md\\",\\n      \\"reason\\": \\"文件不存在\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\"type\\": \\"near_limit\\",\\n      \\"current_lines\\": 178,\\n      \\"limit\\": 200,\\n      \\"action\\": \\"trigger_governance\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\"topic_files\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"file\\": \\"memory_2023_project.md\\",\\n      \\"last_modified\\": \\"2023-11-01\\",\\n      \\"days_since\\": 480,\\n      \\"action\\": \\"archive\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\"skill_issues\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"type\\": \\"duplicate\\",\\n      \\"skills\\": [\\"analyze-stock\\", \\"hk-stock-analysis\\"],\\n      \\"recommendation\\": \\"merge into analyze-hk-stock\\"\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 第二步：生成 MD 治理报告（给用户审批）\\n\\n将 JSON 分析转换为可读 Markdown，写入 `/workspace/memory_governance_report.md`：\\n\\n```markdown\